HEADWORD: magnetic flux density
<hw>magnetic flux density</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The amount of magnetic
flux in a unit area perpendicular to the direction of magnetic
flow.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> magnetic field strength, magnetic intensity,
magnetic induction.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

